INTROS = ["Hello and welcome to the DISC Personality Test! This test isn't just about figuring out who you are; it's about understanding how you communicate and how you can connect better with everyone around you.\n\nBy identifying your primary DISC style—Dominance, Influence, Steadiness, or Conscientiousness—you'll unlock insights into your own communication habits and see how they mesh (or sometimes clash) with others'.\n\nThrough this test you’ll gain insights that enable you to have smoother interactions, more effective communication, and genuinely enjoyable conversation with people of various different communication styles.\n\nWhether in your personal life or at work, knowing your style and understanding others can seriously level up your communication game. Let's get started on this journey to clearer conversation, and easier made connections!"
          ]